WEBVTT

00:06:59.165 --> 00:07:03.248
I guarantee you
that will enrich their life,

00:07:03.272 --> 00:07:04.915
and in turn,

00:07:04.939 --> 00:07:06.317
it will enrich yours.

00:07:07.519 --> 00:07:09.183
And as a bonus,

00:07:09.207 --> 00:07:11.220
one of them may even give a TED Talk.

00:07:11.244 --> 00:07:12.727
(Laughter)

00:07:13.269 --> 00:07:15.634
(Applause)

00:07:18.218 --> 00:07:23.140
We may not be able to solve the bigotry
and the racism of this world today,

00:07:23.164 --> 00:07:26.868
but certainly we can raise children

00:07:27.772 --> 00:07:31.270
to create a positive,
inclusive, connected world